Last updated: 30/01/2025
1. Introduction
AFK Studio ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our "TOZ" mobile application ("App").
2. Information We Collect
2.1 Information You Provide
User preferences and settings
2.2 Automatically Collected Information
App usage statistics and interaction data
Device information and identifiers
Error logs and crash reports
3. How We Use Your Information
Provide and improve our game experience
Analyze app performance and usage patterns
Customize content and user experience
Fix bugs and optimize app functionality
Develop new features and content
Provide customer support
4. Data Storage and Security
Your game data and preferences are stored locally on your device. Any analytics data transmitted to our servers is encrypted and anonymized. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information and do not share personal data with third parties except as described in this policy.
5. Third-Party Services
Firebase Analytics for anonymous usage analysis
Sentry for error tracking and app stability
RevenueCat for in-app purchase management
6. Your Rights
Since your personal data is stored locally on your device, you have complete control over it. You can delete the app at any time to remove all your data. For analytics data, you can contact us to request deletion of any associated anonymous usage data.
7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.